  "texts": [
    "Advanced computer-aided diagnostic systems can greatly enhance the interpretability of medical images, assisting clinicians in making more precise diagnoses and treatment decisions.",
    "The integration of artificial intelligence (AI) into neoadjuvant chemoradiotherapy also improves the treatment outcomes and efficacy assessment in colorectal cancer.",
    "AI offers tremendous opportunities in the era of precision medicine [111].",
    "However, the utilization of AI in healthcare is subject to stringent regulations [112], with only a few AI-based medical devices having received regulatory approval [113].",
    "In comparison to traditional systems, the final stage of innovation in medical AI confronts numerous challenges, with deep learning models often criticized for their \"black box\" issues."
